VI. Invariants

1. Identity Persistence
    Entities remain distinguishable
2. Traceability
    All bindings are auditable
3. Non-Destructive Linking
    Binding ≠ merging (no loss of origin)
4. Consent / Permissions
    Binding must respect boundaries
5. Ethics Gate (≥0.7)
    Mirror + Checksum enforced

